projectDescription: In this project the user gets shown 3 images of products 25 times and selects one each time to find out what the consumer tendencies are.
This project gives us a table of how many cookies were sold in a day and per hour. It is for different cookie stores through out Seattle.
This project is basically what the name says, its about Fortunato Maycotte. It also has a guessing game regarding information about me.
